, did I not write this same text ten years ago? Where is it? It dead-ended
 back then...)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Note that 
\begin_inset Formula $D^{-1}$
\end_inset

 is both a left and right inverse, because Dirichlet convolution is commutative.
\end_layout

