\begin_inset Formula $s^{\prime}$
\end_inset

 for which 
\begin_inset Formula $\zeta\left(s^{\prime}\right)=\zeta\left(s\right)$
\end_inset

.
 But there will always be Hausdorff-separated: there will always be open
